*Niki* je zavoleo fudbal. (Niki loves football.)
Ona je *nikad* ne prestaje da se smeje. (She never stops laughing.)
*Nikog* nisam video. (I didn't see anyone.)
Ona je najbolja *nikom* nije mogao da pomogne. (She's the best. No one could help.)
Njegov *nikakav* plan nije bio dobar. (His any plan was not good.)
*Nikoga* nismo videli. (We didn't see anyone.)